data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath single-family home with the perfect blend of comfort and style. As you step inside, the home welcomes you with an abundance of natural light streaming through well-placed windows, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The living area is perfect for both relaxation and entertaining, with a layout that seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The primary bedroom features an ensuite bath for added convenience and privacy. With two additional bedrooms and another well-appointed bathroom, this home is designed with both functionality and comfort in mind. One of the standout features of this property is the mountain views and grassed fenced-in backyard, providing a private oasis. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Ault property your own.  More pictures to come!
